NHL ENTRY DRAFT
June 26, 1999
Maxime Ouellet
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT
 
 
  
 
  
  
   
 Q. What are your feelings about going to Philadelphia?
 
 MAXIME OUELLET: I'm very happy to go to Philadelphia. I talk with the team a couple of
time, and I'm very happy to be part of this organization.  
 
Q. When you watched the Flyers growing up, did you have a favorite player? 
 
 MAXIME OUELLET: Of course. I'm a goalie, so I know Bernie Parent. He won the cup two
years in a row. He was the best goalie of the Flyers. 
 
